fields.description: We make the cost of TCamp as low as we can to make sure we can be as inclusive as possible, but the reality is that the "fair market value" of each TCamp ticket is more than $130. If you register as a Super Camper, you will not only help cover the actual cost of TCamp, but weâ€™ll toss in some extra bling for you to wear at TCamp!
fields.name: Super Camper

fields.description: As a Camp Counselor, you will help with registration, keep sessions on time, direct lost campers and help with other troubleshooting. If you have a knack for logistics and a friendly customer service demeanor, we need your help! Volunteers must attend an orientation (either online or in person). More details when you sign up! Note: you don't need to also sign up as a camper if you volunteer.
fields.name: Volunteer: Be a Camp Counselor!
